No, you can&#39;t delete a listing, But you can either deactivate it either archive it to clean your catalog display.

To deactivate a listing, you can change the stock of this listing to 0. This will set the listing offline.



If you want to archive a listing you just need to click on &#39;Archive offer&#39;



To see all your archived adds you just need to go on &#39;Archived&#39;
